name: Kitchen Wind Cemento Eta Noir
description: Kitchen Cemento Eta Noir from Toncelli factory, designed Federica Toncelli and Stefano Stefanelli from solid walnut, natural stone, foam and leather. Wooden surface of the unpolished, they deliberately left traces of rough handling in the form of grooves. Elegant kitchen captures crisp, expressive, straight lines. It is presented in two versions - the island and linear (near-wall).
